headlines.description: Sam Ehlinger ran for three touchdowns, the Texas defense largely held Georgia's offense in check, and the Longhorns earned their first 10-win season since 2009 by beating the Bulldogs 28-21 in the Sugar Bowl on Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ehlinger's 3 TDs lead Texas past Georgia 28-21 in Sugar Bowl

events.name: Washington Huskies at Ohio State Buckeyes

notes.headline: Rose Bowl Game Pres. by Northwestern Mutual

headlines.description: Dwayne Haskins passed for 251 yards and three touchdowns, and Urban Meyer finished his coaching career at Ohio State with a 28-23 victory after the Buckeyes held off Washington's thrilling fourth-quarter comeback in the 105th Rose Bowl on Tuesday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ohio State tops Washington 28-23 in Meyer's Rose Bowl finale

video.headline: Meyer wins Rose Bowl in farewell with Buckeyes

headlines.description: Joe Burrow shook off a vicious early hit to throw for 394 yards and four touchdowns, helping No. 11 LSU end No. 7 Central Florida's 25-game winning streak with a 40-32 victory in the Fiesta Bowl on Tuesday.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 11 LSU knocks off No. 7 UCF 40-32 in Fiesta Bowl

video.headline: Burrow hangs tough, tosses four TDs in LSU win

headlines.description: Safety Jake Gervase made an interception in the end zone to help preserve a late lead, and ball-hawking Iowa Hawkeyes beat No. 18 Mississippi State in the Outback Bowl 27-22 Tuesday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Iowa rallies past No. 18 Mississippi State in Outback Bowl
